YOU'RE GOING ?
TO SEE THE PERSONNEL MANAGER.

67
00:07:30,583 --> 00:07:32,585
I'M THE MANAGER.
WE'RE NOT HIRING ANYONE.

68
00:07:33,085 --> 00:07:36,589
WELL, I WAS JUST SPEAKING
TO MR. BIGGLEY.
BIGGLEY ?  J.B. BIGGLEY ?

69
00:07:36,589 --> 00:07:38,591
YES, SIR.
HE TOLD ME TO SEE YOU.

70
00:07:38,591 --> 00:07:43,095
