ON FRIENDSHIP TO GET A JOB.

72
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:51,103
BY GEORGE, I LIKE A MAN
WHO STANDS ON HIS OWN TWO FEET.

73
00:07:51,103 --> 00:07:54,106
MY NAME IS BRATT.  YOU'RE--
