I'M GOING TO THE BARBER SHOP
TO GET A SCALP MASSAGE.

99
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:21,644
AT THIS TIME
OF THE MORNING ?  WHY ?
BECAUSE I'M THE BOSS'S NEPHEW.

100
