OH, BUD.

103
00:09:28,618 --> 00:09:31,621
THIS IS BUD FRUMP,
MR. BIGGLEY'S NEPHEW.
SAY HELLO TO OUR NEW MR. FINCH.

104
00:09:31,621 --> 00:09:33,623
HE'LL BE WORKING WITH YOU
IN THE MAIL ROOM.

105
00:09:33,623 --> 00:09:36,626
HELLO, FINCH.
I'M BUD FRUMP,
MR. BIGGLEY'S NEPHEW.

