WORRY ABOUT BUD FRUMP.

119
00:10:14,163 --> 00:10:17,166
EVERY COMPANY HAS A COUPLE
OF RELATIVES FLOATING AROUND.

120
00:10:17,166 --> 00:10:20,169
SMITTY, YOU WERE GOING
TO GET MR. FINCH'S
VITAL STATISTICS.

121
00:10:20,169 --> 00:10:22,672
