ARE YOU QUITE FINISHED
WITH MR. FINCH ?
FOR THE MOMENT.

131
00:10:55,204 --> 00:10:58,708
IRVING !  TAKE MR. FINCH
TO THE MAIL ROOM AND INTRODUCE
HIM TO MR. TWIMBLE.

132
00:10:58,708 --> 00:11:01,210
