TAKES A COMBINATION OF SKILL,
DIPLOMACY...

183
00:15:15,881 --> 00:15:17,883
AND BOLD CAUTION.

184
00:15:19,385 --> 00:15:21,387
?? WHEN I JOINED THIS FIRM ??

185
00:15:21,387 --> 00:15:23,389
?? AS A BRASH YOUNG MAN ??

186
