HMM ?

780
00:53:33,677 --> 00:53:37,180
I-- I DIDN'T REALIZE
THAT I WAS HUMMING, SIR.

781
00:53:37,180 --> 00:53:40,684
YOU WERE HUMMING
THE OLD IVY FIGHT SONG.

782
00:53:40,684 --> 00:53:42,686
DID YOU GO THERE ?
