WITH HER ALL ALONG !

1207
01:20:37,232 --> 01:20:40,735
YOU FOUND OUT YOU WERE
IN LOVE WITH ROSEMARY
BY KISSING ME ?

1208
01:20:40,735 --> 01:20:45,240
- YES, YES.
- "IT IS A FAR, FAR BETTER
   THING I DO...

