01:22:03,318 --> 01:22:06,321
?? GIVE ME MORE OF THE SAME ??

1227
01:22:09,824 --> 01:22:12,327
?? ROSEMARY ??

1228
01:22:15,330 --> 01:22:18,333
?? ROSEMARY ??

1229
01:22:18,333 --> 01:22:20,835
??
