1245
01:23:15,890 --> 01:23:18,393
[ Chuckles ]
WELL,
WHAT'S THE MATTER ?

1246
01:23:19,894 --> 01:23:21,896
ROSEMARY.
DON'T LET ME KEEP YOU.
GO ON !

1247
01:23:21,896 --> 01:23:24,899
